		<span id="title-175695295" class="story-title"> <a   href="//it.slashdot.org/story/24/12/18/173242/australia-moves-to-drop-some-cryptography-by-2030">Australia Moves To Drop Some Cryptography By 2030</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.theregister.com/2024/12/17/australia_dropping_crypto_keys/"  title="External link - https://www.theregister.com/2024/12/17/australia_dropping_crypto_keys/" target="_blank"> (theregister.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
